# MCP server keys — stored in .claude/settings.local.json (gitignored, never commit)
# LINEAR_API_KEY        → linear.app → Settings → API → Personal API keys
# NOTION_API_TOKEN      → notion.so/my-integrations → New integration → Internal Integration Token
# SLACK_BOT_TOKEN       → api.slack.com/apps → OAuth & Permissions → Bot Token (xoxb-...)
# SLACK_TEAM_ID         → Slack workspace URL: app.slack.com/client/TXXXXXXXX → that T-code
